item.title: CVE-2023-3153|2023-10-04T11:13:40.083Z -- n%2Fa -- ovn
item.description: A flaw was found in Open Virtual Network where the service monitor MAC does not properly rate limit. This issue could allow an attacker to cause a denial of service, including on deployments with CoPP enabled and properly configured.
